title: UDEMY TWITTER MARKETING FOR BUSINESS BUILD LOYALTY IN FOLLOWERS
description:
Course Description

Are you frustrated because you work hard to get twitter followers and they end up unfollowing you? Do you want to make more money from your twitter promotions? Do you want your followers seek out your tweets from their huge twitter feeds?

The connection you build with your twitter followers is so much more important that just the number of followers you have. Would you rather have 10 sales from 1,500 twitter followers or 3 sales from 25,000 followers? I would rather have more sales, wouldn't you?
